snippet.title: Top 10 Things You Didn't Know About Bad Bunny
snippet.description:
From bagging groceries to breaking Billboard records! Join us as we dive into surprising facts about Latin music's global phenomenon. Did you know he almost performed wearing a bunny mask? Or that he's a WWE Champion? Our countdown explores the journey of Benito Antonio Martínez Ocasio to international superstardom. We cover everything from his Gekkō restaurant in Miami, to his historic Grammy nomination, to being Spotify's most-streamed artist for three consecutive years. We even reveal the childhood photo that inspired his iconic stage name. What's your favorite Bad Bunny song? Let us know in the comments!
